oxe EPR etc. sont autant d’expériences et de concepts qui sont décrits dans cet ouvrage.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Apr 2022) 0aQuantum theory. 4aGeneral Physics. 7aSCIENCE / Physics / General.2bisacsh1 aZarate, Oscar, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEDP Sciences Backlist eBook Package 2001 - 2015z978311075641840uhttps://doi.org/10.1051/978-2-7598-1697-240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782759816972423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782759816972/original  a978-3-11-075641-8  EDP Sciences Backlist eBook Package 2001 - 2015c2001d2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MTPY  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK